Package: lstmohi
Type: Package
Title: Land Surface Temperature from Landsat 8 Images
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gulam Mohiuddin
Maintainer: Gulam Mohiuddin <mohigeo33@gmail.com>
Description: The package calculates land surface temperature by calling simple functions after introducing band 10, band 5 and band 4 from Landsat 8 images.It also calcuate the intermediate indices like normalized difference vegetation index, radiance, emissivity and temperature brightness.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
